channel.title: [Request] Auto fisher + Banker
channel.description:
I was wondering if someone could make me an auto fisher, to fish lobbies in taverly, then bank them. If you can make it anti-random, so it runs whenever there is a random, also, so it collects the cage if it is taken and thrown by the fish that pops up every once in a while.
Thanks, and good luck.
